Alternatively, you can connect the cables while the participant wears the cap. To do this, carefully lift the cap at the chosen 10-10 position, and place the electrode directly underneath. The electrode knob should be sticking out, so that you can attach the clip cable to it on the outside. Repeat for the remaining electrodes.
